### Events API Testing

### Get all events
GET https://localhost:7083/api/events

### Get all planned events
GET https://localhost:7083/api/events?status=Planned

### Get event by ID
GET https://localhost:7083/api/events/1

### Create new event
POST https://localhost:7083/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "New Event",
  "customerId": 2,
  "roomId": 2,
  "status": "Planned"
}

### Update event
PUT https://localhost:7083/api/events/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Event",
  "customerId": 1,
  "roomId": 3,
  "status": "Ongoing"
}

### Delete event
DELETE https://localhost:7083/api/events/3

